headline.main: Technology Added to Ring in 1984 View of Boxing

results.snippet: FOUR hours before the fight, Sonny (the Secaucus Smasher) Clayvich swallowed an electronic device no larger than an aspirin tablet, as did his opponent. In the dressing room, a former astronaut, now deputy chairman of the Federal Boxing Commission,...
results.lead_paragraph: FOUR hours before the fight, Sonny (the Secaucus Smasher) Clayvich swallowed an electronic device no larger than an aspirin tablet, as did his opponent. In the dressing room, a former astronaut, now deputy chairman of the Federal Boxing Commission, checked the transistors buried in the padding of each fighter's gloves.
